http://weather.geo.nsf.gov

   ATM UNIDATA

                               ATM Weather Server

   [colorbar.gif]

   This server provides up to the minute weather information for NSF
   employees and visitors.
     * Satellite/Radar Images
     * Weather around Washington, D.C.
     * Weather around the U.S.
     * Other Weather Related links

   [colorbar.gif]

   The products displayed here are generated automatically as the data are
   received via the Internet Data Distribution (IDD) system. Radar
   products are provided by WSI. Contact Cliff Jacobs <cjacobs@nsf.gov> at
   NSF for more information.
